94f65381736ec13cb9091","tid":1664053,"uid":110110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T21:29:03.000Z","msg":"同裝修有分級制一樣 都係要按比例<br />\n另外就係要諗吓點樣解決去死一間黃店嘅問題<br />\n我屋企樓下間加藤屋已經排咗幾個月隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaeac68751b793715bbc8257029a8d94624884f","tid":1664053,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1ed20d95368e027e46448077381c5008526eea","tid":1664053,"uid":29052,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T20:43:56.000Z","msg":"級制硬係覺得好反感&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾錢升級既感覺 好似去咗傳銷&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:33:03.000Z","msg":"唔比錢、用電視放映係最高級。<br />\n而且捐都係一個月捐一日，對黃店老闆唔算太過分要求掛。"},{"pid":"b3d8ae3b79a71a10b4dd080c7265c4306a08ea19","tid":1664053,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ca2fdd24223df05e609dcc38eb179506f58c2e7","tid":1664053,"uid":132641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"add81cffc3ddc65d1f2ab7b1a9d04704ceff5fca","tid":1664053,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0HNqmq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0HNqmq.jpg&h=976316bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"571199259f9b1e1764f6a0d8335a5ec1ed333274","tid":1664053,"uid":100363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"推 五大訴求 缺一不可 自衛反擊 香港人 反抗 撤回已不是重點 解散警隊 追究刑責 勿忘721 85 811 831警黑勾結 無差別恐襲 10月1港殤"},{"pid":"09a2f2cceb616ecd626260fd1a9266882fac307d","tid":1664053,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:44:37.0